institution: Human Resources Development Service of Korea
category: Skill Competition Management Rules/Article 22 (Administrative management according to processing of objections, etc.)
contents: Article 22 (Administrative management according to processing of objections, etc.) ① The head judge must prepare an objection processing status (Form No. 25) for objections raised during the game and submit all materials related to the objection after the end of the game. ② Complaints regarding objections to game progress and scoring results received through the corporation's electronic complaint processing system will be processed in accordance with the corporation's customer rights protection rules.
